        "title": "Fix CLI and plugin edge-case bugs",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Clawpatch-assisted bug sweep across CLI, browser, gateway history, ACP permissions, node host, secrets, and first-party plugins.\n- Tightens malformed timeout/numeric option parsing, media extension/base64 bounds, remote URL redaction, JSON output shape, TLS pin inheritance, plugin manifest preservation, and imported history dedupe/order.\n- Prevents several stuck or leaked runtime paths in progress rendering, Codex app-server writes/parsing, IRC aborts, Synology rate limiting/user-list fetches, Twitch connection readiness/retry/shutdown, and Signal API auto-detection.\n- Adds focused regression coverage for the accepted current-source bugs.\n\n## Verification\n\nBehavior addressed: CLI/plugin edge cases found by `../clawpatch` and follow-up review: malformed values accepted, stale config/metadata reused, unsafe media paths, duplicate JSON output, stuck waits, duplicate/leaked Twitch clients, and imported history merge loss.\nReal environment tested: local source checkout on `bugfix/clawpatch-sweep-cli-runtime`, rebased on current `origin/main`.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/cli/parse-timeout.test.ts src/cli/update-cli/shared.command-runner.test.ts src/cli/progress.test.ts src/cli/completion-cli.test.ts src/cli/profile.test.ts src/cli/plugins-authoring-command.test.ts src/gateway/cli-session-history.test.ts extensions/twitch/src/twitch-client.test.ts extensions/irc/src/send.test.ts src/cli/nodes-camera.test.ts src/cli/cron-cli/register.cron-edit.test.ts src/cli/update-cli.option-collisions.test.ts src/acp/client.test.ts extensions/signal/src/client-adapter.test.ts extensions/browser/src/cli/browser-cli-manage.test.ts src/cli/secrets-cli.test.ts src/cli/node-cli/register.test.ts && pnpm tsgo && git diff --check`\nEvidence after fix: 19 test files passed, 307 tests passed; `pnpm tsgo` completed; `git diff --check` completed.\nObserved result after fix: focused regression suite, typecheck